Cactus is a plant in the Farming skill. Level 55 farmers may grow a cactus by planting a cactus seed in a cactus patch using a seed dibber. The nearby farmer will watch over a growing cactus tree in exchange for 6 cadava berries which may be noted to save inventory space.

A cactus may take 9 hours to mature. Once mature, the cactus produces 3 or more cactus spines at a time. Once any of the cactus spines have been picked, the cactus will slowly produce more until all 3 or more are available again. It takes around 25 minutes for another cactus spine to grow.

Planting a cactus seed in a cactus patch grants 66.5 Farming experience. Checking the health of a cactus grants 374 Farming experience. Harvesting each cactus spine grants 25 Farming experience.
